OL,3,CMayoral elections: Tories face crunch
OL,4,Cvotes in key battlegrounds
OL,6,FBy Maya Bowles, Westminster Producer
OL,8,FOn May 2, people across England and
OL,9,FWales will go to the polls to vote in
OL,10,Flocal elections - the biggest test for
OL,11,Fthe government ahead of an expected
OL,12,Fgeneral election this year.
OL,14,FPeople will vote to elect councillors,
OL,15,Fmayors, and police and crime
OL,16,Fcommissioners, with 2,636 council
OL,17,Fseats up for grabs, along with 10
OL,18,Fmayoral positions.
