OL,6,FMost of these positions were last
OL,7,Ffought in 2021, when the Conservatives
OL,8,Fenjoyed a positive local election
OL,9,Fperformance after the success of the
OL,10,Fvaccine rollout.
OL,12,FWhile the Tories are 20 points behind
OL,13,FLabour in the polls nationally, two
OL,14,Fkey votes on Thursday are much closer
OL,15,Fto call - they're the Tees Valley and
OL,16,FWest Midlands mayoral elections.
OL,18,FIf the Conservatives lose one or even
OL,19,Fboth of their mayors, it could have a
OL,20,Fserious impact on Rishi Sunak's
OL,21,Fstrength as leader of the party.
