OL,6,FKnown as "metro mayors", they have
OL,7,Fspecific responsibilities in their
OL,8,Fareas which are separate from the
OL,9,Fcouncil and central government,
OL,10,Fincluding economic development,
OL,11,Ftransport, and culture and tourism.
OL,13,FBoth Mr Houchen and Mr Street have
OL,14,Fdistanced themselves from the
OL,15,FConservative Party in their campaigns,
OL,16,Ffocussing more on their individual
OL,17,Fachievements and ambitions.
