OL,6,FHis election in 2017 marked the
OL,7,Fbeginning of the difficulties that lay
OL,8,Fahead for Labour in its so-called "red
OL,9,Fwall".
OL,11,FMade a Lord in 2023 through Former
OL,12,FPrime Minister Johnson's resignation
OL,13,Fhonours list, Mr Houchen is also known
OL,14,Fas "Baron Houchen of High Level".
