OL,6,FMr Houchen resisted the
OL,7,Fcharacterisation of the vote in Tees
OL,8,FValley as a representation of the
OL,9,Fpopularity of the Conservatives,
OL,10,Ftelling ITV News: "This is a local
OL,11,Felection, it's about who's going to be
OL,12,Fthe next mayor, who's going to
OL,13,Fcontinue to create jobs, bring
OL,14,Finvestment into our public transport
OL,15,Fsystem."
