OL,6,FDespite this, he played down his
OL,7,Fprospects of victory in the mayoral
OL,8,Frace, acknowledging "there's an
OL,9,Fincredible mountain to climb".
OL,11,FThe Liberal Democrats didn't stand in
OL,12,FTees Valley last time, but they're
OL,13,Fhoping to make gains on Thursday.
OL,15,FSimon Thorley, who runs an
