OL,6,FWest Midlands
OL,8,FFormer managing director of John
OL,9,FLewis, Andy Street was elected as the
OL,10,Ffirst mayor of the West Midlands in
OL,11,F2017, narrowly beating Labour.
OL,13,FHe's managed to hold onto his post
OL,14,Fever since, after successfully
OL,15,Fdefending it at the 2021 election
OL,16,Fwhere he increased his margin of
OL,17,Fvictory.
