OL,6,FAnne-Marie Alder, who runs a food bank
OL,7,Fat Bells Farm Community Centre in
OL,8,FBirmingham, says their footfall has
OL,9,F"massively increased" recently amid
OL,10,Fthe cost of living crisis and council
OL,11,Fcuts.
OL,13,FShe believes people struggling locally
OL,14,Fwill vote with their feet over the
OL,15,Fdwindling council services and
OL,16,Fquestioned why more hadn't been done
OL,17,Fto save the council from financial
OL,18,Fcrisis, asking: "Why's it been allowed
OL,19,Fto go on so long?"
