OL,6,F"You only hear of Andy Street because
OL,7,Fhe's here there and everywhere at the
OL,8,Fmoment but what are these mayors
OL,9,Flooking at doing for our community?
OL,10,FIt's been under regeneration for 15
OL,11,Fyears and we still haven't put a brick
OL,12,Fon the floor," Ms Alder questioned.
OL,14,F"What's he doing for our community?
OL,15,FAbsolutely nothing."
OL,17,FBut she doesn't place all the blame
OL,18,Fwith Mr Street and pointed to failings
OL,19,Fin central government.
