OL,7,FBirmingham are very, very separate to
OL,8,Fthe finances of the West Midlands as a
OL,9,Fwhole."
OL,11,FDespite being a Conservative for
OL,12,Fdecades, his links to the Party are
OL,13,Fnowhere to be seen on his Twitter bio
OL,14,Fwhich describes the West Midlands as
OL,15,F"the best region in the world". Nor is
