OL,7,FMidlands Mayor rejected speculation
OL,8,Fthat he's distancing himself from the
OL,9,FConservative Party and that his
OL,10,Fmayoral campaigning has always been
OL,11,Fcentred around his personal brand.
OL,13,F"If you look at how I conducted myself
